text: The True Story of Eskimo Nell (retitled Dick Down Under in the United KingdomIMDb Trivia) is a 1975 Australian western comedy movie directed by first time director Richard Franklin and starring Max Gillies, Serge Lazareff, Butcher Vachon, Kris McQuade, Grahame Bond, Ernie Bourne, Elke Neidhardt. == References == ==Other websites== * Category:1975 comedy movies Category:1970s Western (genre) movies Category:Australian Western (genre) movies Category:Australian comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Richard Franklin
title: The True Story of Eskimo Nell
